  <brief_title>FiO2 in Chronic Obstructive Pulmonary Disease (COPD) Patient Normobaric O2 Versus NIV</brief_title>
  <acronym>NIVLEAKS</acronym>
  <official_title>Measured FiO2 With Nasal Canula O2 Versus Noninvasive Ventilation (NIV) With the Same O2 Flow, in COPD Patients the NIV LEAKS Study</official_title>
